 Sphink and his fellow destron where disgusted at the sight. They could not 
bieleve that thier king refused to join in this peace symbol. They decided to 
ignore his motion not to do it. They knew that the ark was unimportant to 
their kind. But if they wanted to make a peaceful alliance with the maximals 
then they better at least try to be civilized. They turned back to the 
floating bot.
